---
title: (Vegetarian) Roast Cauliflower Biryani with Currants & Roasted Almonds
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the rice itself is cooked with the curry paste? Now that’s magical. Studded with sweet rich currants, fresh coriander and roasted cauliflower, this is curry as you’ve never experienced it before.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6a3dcb30006c0ceb0191f4-3641081a.jpg
